// Semantic direction:
// formaterer enforces a single canonical code style, eliminating style debates from code review.
// format_diff shows proposed changes without applying them, enabling pre-commit review.
// format_sjekk returns a non-zero exit code if any file differs from the formatted version (CI use).
// importsortering groups imports by orden (stdlib first, external packages second, internal last).
// lint_regler_sett is a named configuration like "streng", "anbefalt", or "minimal".
// syklomatisk_kompleksitet counts decision points in a function; high values indicate refactoring need.
// duplikat_kode identifies structurally similar code blocks across different locations.
// lint_ignorer_linje suppresses a specific regel violation for one line via a comment annotation.
// repl_løkke implements the Read-Eval-Print loop: prompt → parse → eval → print → repeat.
// persistent_kontekst accumulates all definitions entered in the session; later expressions see prior ones.
// repl_omdefiner replaces a previous binding, updating the kontekst without clearing history.
// kommando_type shows the inferred type of an expression without evaluating it fully.
// kommando_vis_ast renders the parsed abstract syntax tree for a given expression.
// kommando_vis_bytekode disassembles the compiled bytecode for inspection and learning.
// kommando_tidsberegning wraps evaluation with a timer to measure expression performance.
// fuzzy_fullføring ranks completion candidates by edit distance to the partial input.

// Primitive flow:
// formaterer: les kilde -> parse til AST -> pretty_print(AST, stil_konfig)
//   sammenlign med original -> diff? -> skriv ny versjon | format_sjekk: exit(1)
//   mellomrom_rundt_operatorer: a+b -> a + b; importsortering: stdlib < ekstern < intern
// linter: lint_kjør(prosjekt) -> for hvert fil: parse -> traverser AST
//   ubrukt_variabel: binding definert, aldri lest -> lint_brudd(fil, linje, forslag: "fjern")
//   syklomatisk: tell if/while/for/match-grener -> > grense: lint_brudd(alvorlighet_advarsel)
// repl: repl_start -> vis velkomst -> repl_løkke:
//   "> " prompt -> les linje -> parse -> sjekk om komplett uttrykk
//   komplett: evaluer i repl_miljø -> repl_skriv_ut(resultat + type)
//   ":type x": kommando_type -> inference(x) -> vis type uten side-effekter
//   tab: repl_autofullføring -> fuzzy_fullføring(delprefiks, kontekst) -> vis liste

// This defines language tooling: opinionated code formatter with import sorting, a comprehensive
// linter with cyclomatic complexity and duplicate detection, and a full-featured REPL with
// persistent context, autocomplete, and inspector commands.
